{
  "stem": "7506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that person would be told that tomorrow morning at 6 o'clock, or 5 o'clock, or whatever time, they had to be in a certain part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, while I was there I saw different trains leaving there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the same place as we had arrived, I saw trains leaving, in those days steam trains, of course, pulled by locomotives leaving from Westerbork and all cattle cars, only cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never saw a normal train leave there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, children are usually excited about railroads and trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you feel any such excitement?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I had, by already that age in my life, been a quite frequent traveler between Holland and England by ship, I've always been fascinated by travel and the world.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was less fascinated by travel after being taken from Amsterdam east in the train to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never excited about those trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must have felt-- I must have felt at the time-- some sort of ominous feeling about those trains, because I had never, until that first time, done any of my traveling in a car that was meant for cattle.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure I must have been, as I was then, nearly 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must have had forebodings about that mode of travel, to put it in a nice way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do remember, and it's been a terrible thing to me in my life, remembering that I saw one of my uncles being in the train, being in one of those cattle cars, and those cattle cars on the top, in certain parts of its four walls, have little grills.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember seeing my Uncle Max, who was an uncle of mine called Max Rabbie.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
